Enter "aws.amazon.com" into browser
Sign into Thorsten's Amazon Web Services account
	Click "Sign In to the Console"
Enter Thorsten's account information
	I'm using "thorsten.lehr@..."
Click "Services"
Click EC2
	Takes you into the console

Note: The console will primarily be used for creating instances, and sometimes for managing security groups.

Definition of an Instance: http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/ec2-instances-and-amis.html
Definition of Security Groups: http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/using-network-security.html
